  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "div",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "name"
   },
   "html": "\n[ こだま・げんたろう ]"
  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "div",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "prof"
   },
   "html": "\n陸相、内相、文相、参謀総長、台湾総督、満州軍総参謀長、南満州鉄道株式会社創立委員長、陸軍大将"
  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "table",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "lt"
   },
   "html": "<tbody><tr><td class=\"lt\"><a href=\"02k.html\">一覧　（カ）</a></td><td class=\"lt\"><a href.html\"=\"\">　</a></td><td class=\"lt\"><a href=\"http://www.amazon.co.jp/exec/obidos/redirect?link_code=ur2&amp;tag=click20thcetu-22&amp;camp=247&amp;creative=1211&amp;path=external-search%3Fsearch-type=ss%26index=blended%26keyword=%25E5%2585%2590%25E7%258E%2589%2520%25E6%25BA%2590%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E9%2583%258E\" target=\"_blank\">本を入手</a><img src=\"http://www.assoc-amazon.jp/e/ir?t=click20thcetu-22&amp;l=ur2&amp;o=9\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"border:none !important; margin:0px !important;\"></td><td class=\"lt\"><a href.html\"=\"\">　</a></td></tr></tbody>"
  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "div",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "off"
   },
   "html": "<span class=\"m_r\">エピソード 1</span>調査中。"
  },
  {
   "type": "timeline",
   "rows": [
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　徳山藩士。戊辰戦争に従軍。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　維新後陸軍に入り、士族反乱の鎮圧に活躍。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　陸大校長として近代軍制整備に尽力。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　ヨーロッパ視察後、日清戦争では大本営陸軍参謀。その後、台湾総督。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　日露戦争には満州軍総参謀長として出征。<a href=\"../1904/11ryojy.html\">旅順総攻撃③</a>では陣頭指揮も執る。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　戦後、満鉄設立委員長となるも、就任直後に病没。"
      }
     ]
    }
   ]
  },
